'''Michael Slovis''' is an American director and cinematographer for film and television. He is best known for his work on ''Law and Order: SVU'', ''Elementary'', ''Chicago Fire'', ''CSI'', and was the cinematographer for ''Breaking Bad''. He also previously directed [[Nikolaj Coster-Waldau]]'s 2008 TV series ''New Amsterdam''.

On July 2, 2014, it was announced that Slovis will be directing two episodes in the [[Season 5|fifth season]], the season premiere and the second episode.&lt;ref&gt;[http://winteriscoming.net/2014/07/02/michael-slovis-joins-the-lineup-of-directors-for-game-of-thrones-season-5/#comment-420830 Michael Slovis joins the lineup of directors for Game of Thrones season 5]&lt;/ref&gt;
